  "title": "⚡🚀 SALES EXECUTIVE – ENTRY LEVEL 🚀",
  "description": "<p>Training Provided | High Commission | Uncapped Earnings | Career Advancement</p><p>🌟 START YOUR SALES CAREER WITH US!</p><p>If you want:</p><p>To earn based on your performance</p><p>To develop valuable sales and communication skills</p><p>To grow quickly with clear advancement paths</p><p>To work with a motivated and supportive team</p><p>This role is for you.</p><p>👥 WHO CAN APPLY?</p><p>Fresh graduates eager to learn</p><p>ORD personnel ready to build a career</p><p>Career changers seeking growth</p><p>Anyone with a positive mindset and willingness to improve</p><p>No prior experience necessary — training is provided.</p><p>🎯 YOUR RESPONSIBILITIES</p><p>Build relationships with potential customers</p><p>Understand customer needs and provide solutions</p><p>Present products confidently</p><p>Overcome objections professionally</p><p>Close sales and follow up</p><p>📚 TRAINING & DEVELOPMENT</p><p>Comprehensive onboarding and coaching</p><p>Sales techniques and product training</p><p>Daily mentoring by experienced leaders</p><p>Continuous feedback to support growth</p><p>💸 EARNINGS & BENEFITS</p><p>Performance-based commissions</p><p>Unlimited earning potential</p><p>Incentives and rewards for high performers</p><p>📈 CAREER PROGRESSION</p><p>Sales Executive</p><p>Senior Sales Executive</p><p>Team Leader</p><p>Sales Manager</p><p>Promotions based on results and leadership.</p><p>🤝 TEAM CULTURE</p><p>Supportive and dynamic environment</p><p>Team bonding events</p><p>Recognition for achievements</p><p>Mentorship from experienced leaders</p><p>🚫 WHO SHOULD NOT APPLY</p><p>Those seeking fixed salary without pressure</p><p>Those unwilling to be accountable</p><p>Those avoiding performance-based work</p><p>👉 CALL TO ACTION</p><p>🔥 DM “EXEC” or apply today!</p><p>🔥 Limited slots available</p><p>Take the first step to a rewarding sales career.</p>",
